giải nghĩa từ "coworkers" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan
coworkers /ˈkoʊˌwɜːrkərz/ (noun)
* Meaning: people who work together in the same organization or on the same project
* Vietnamese translation: đồng nghiệp (noun)

Example sentence: "My coworkers are very supportive and helpful."

Related words:

* colleague (noun): a person who works with you in the same organization or department
* team member (noun): a person who is part of a team working together on a project or task
* associate (noun): a person who works with you in a business or organization, but may not be directly involved in the same project or task

Note: The term "coworkers" is often used to refer to people who work together in a collaborative or team-based environment, whereas "colleagues" may refer to people who work in the same organization or department, but may not necessarily work together on the same project or task.
